Next city is \(fresno). It is \(distanceToFresno)km from \(yose).
Population is \(populationOfFresno) people.
Our expenses:
\(totalGasFresno)$ on gas.
\(totalFoodFresno)$ on food.
\(totalHotelFresno)$ on a hotel.

""")

var totalGasTrip = totalGasLA + totalGasYose + totalGasFresno + totalGasTahoe + totalGasSanFr + totalGasMonterey + totalGasSanLO
